
    calculating ciphertext size

course of action
    1. check all ciphers and their specifications in libgcrypt

information requirements
    1. does it change ciphertext size?

results
    doc/results.pdf

GCM (Galois/Counter Mode)
    Increases length due to authentication tag (typically 16 bytes).
CCM (Counter with CBC-MAC)
    Increases length due to authentication tag (8-16 bytes).
